## Key Arch Decisions

- Blazor Server (not WASM) — server-side rendering, simpler auth flow
- Azure AD B2C for external user auth (different from Alpha's internal AD)
- Fixed-price contract: aggressive agentization (70% target)
- Budget: $20/sprint, cost alert per spec $2.00
- Requires tech lead approval for agent runs

## Agentization

